# collisionspike core

- Start at `README.md` and `docs/README.md`.
- Tickets and plans are work authority. Binding reviews override earlier written
  requirements in the areas they cover.
- `LIVE_FACTS.json` and `docs/operations/live-environment.md` are state authority.
- Run `npm run verify` for the offline gate. Live reads require the matching skill
  and current task authority; production writes require explicit approval.
- The parser engine is authored in `services/engine/cedocumentmapper_v2/` and materialized into
  `services/functions/parser` and `services/functions/ocr`; do not hand-edit a materialized copy or
  rederive the engine elsewhere.
- Production web code may load only real REST data. Fabricated records belong in
  test fixtures and must never be importable by production modules.
